# ── SwiftData / CoreData stores ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# These live in the app sandbox (simulator or device) and are never in the
# project directory — but guard here in case any are accidentally exported.
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.store

# ── Secrets & config ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
